=== Basic Character Matching ===
abc	 ~ 	abc		true
abc	 ~ 	abd		false

=== Kleene Star (*) ===
bc	 ~ 	a*bc		true
abc	 ~ 	a*bc		true
aabc	 ~ 	a*bc		true
	 ~ 	a*		true
a	 ~ 	a*		true
aaa	 ~ 	a*		true
abc	 ~ 	a*b*c*		true
aaabbbccc	 ~ 	a*b*c*		true

=== Optional (?) ===
ac	 ~ 	ab?c		true
abc	 ~ 	ab?c		true
abbc	 ~ 	ab?c		false

=== Alternation (|) ===
a	 ~ 	a|b		true
b	 ~ 	a|b		true
c	 ~ 	a|b		false
ab	 ~ 	ab|cd		true
cd	 ~ 	ab|cd		true
ac	 ~ 	ab|cd		false

=== Complex Patterns ===
	 ~ 	(a|b)*		true
a	 ~ 	(a|b)*		true
ab	 ~ 	(a|b)*		true
aba	 ~ 	(a|b)*		true
c	 ~ 	(a|b)*		false

=== Should Fail ===
abc	 ~ 	abcd		false
a	 ~ 	ab		false
